  "title": "Regional E-Commerce Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role:</strong><br>\nWe’re seeking an experienced <strong>Regional E-Commerce Executive</strong> to manage and grow our online appliance sales across Southeast Asia. You’ll oversee marketplace operations, launch impactful campaigns, and use data-driven strategies to boost sales and customer engagement.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage e-commerce platforms and ensure listings, inventory, and product content are optimised.</li>\n  <li>Plan and run major online campaigns, including sales events and new product launches.</li>\n  <li>Analyse performance metrics and recommend actions to maximise sales and ROI.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with regional and local teams to align strategies and enhance visibility.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Marketing, Business, E-Commerce, or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>3–5 years’ experience in managing e-commerce operations across multiple markets.</li>\n  <li>Strong analytical skills and a proven track record of online sales success.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
